BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-plotrix 
BuildRequires:    R-utils 
Requires:         R-graphics 
Requires:         R-CRAN-plotrix 
Requires:         R-utils 

%description
Within the area of movement ecology, it can be useful to identify an
animal's sites of interest. These will be places that an animal uses a lot
and so will spend a proportionately longer time there. The aim of this
package is to identify both the position and size of these sites of
interest from high resolution (sub-second) positional data.

